<page section="release-3.8.0">
  <heading>Release 3.8.0</heading>

  <content>
    <para>
      <release-info version="3.8.0" />
      The 3.8.0 release fixes a number of bugs fixes and updates library dependencies.
    </para>

    <table class="release-notes">
      <tr>
        <td class="head">
          Bug fixes and improvements
        </td>

        <td>
          <p>
            A number of minor bug fixes and tweaks have been patched. These affected the DCS,
            ETools, bisecting k-means and Bing document source.
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td class="head">
          Third party library updates
        </td>

        <td>
          <p>
            Morfologik 1.7, simplexml 2.7, HPPC 0.5.2.
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <hr />

    <p>
      For a complete list of improvements and bug fixes, see <a href="http://goo.gl/pPSpMy">JIRA</a> 
    </p>
  </content>
</page>

